data.description: Great New Price! $390K Vista Too, a 55-age, Doublewide manufactured home with land. This home is single level featuring 1,728square feet Primary Bedroom with full bathroom, separate shower & walk-in closet. Living & Family enjoy a multi-room floor plan. The flow from room to room is easy & gentle. The eat-in kitchen has walk through access to both living areas. Family Rm served as the TV room. The Living Rm hosts the Dining Rm & formal sitting areas. 2 additional bedrooms share a full bath serving the remainder of the home. We have a 2-car detached garage & plenty of parking near the entrance to the home. Our covered patio has access to the treed green belt areas, perfect for your barbeques. New Roof being installed, adding Huge VALUE.
